name: Scouts of the Anuran Birth
description: Hailing from the Bogs of the <Anuran Countryside>, the Scouts of the Anuran Birth are known for their stewardship of unripe Fruit Folk, and assisting with incubation when necessary. Now guiding travelers that attempt to cross the continent in the dead of night, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
